WEBVTT

00:01:08.600 --> 00:01:09.360
Stop!

00:01:14.280 --> 00:01:15.160
Yiyu!

00:01:17.240 --> 00:01:18.320
Sinan!

00:01:19.960 --> 00:01:21.320
It's my fault.

00:01:21.640 --> 00:01:23.570
I've caused you so much suffering.

00:01:25.160 --> 00:01:26.820
Nothing happened last night.

00:01:26.960 --> 00:01:28.440
I knocked Liu Silin unconscious

00:01:28.440 --> 00:01:29.700
and managed to escape.

00:01:31.600 --> 00:01:32.640
This is...

00:01:33.479 --> 00:01:35.479
This is the new servant at the Liu residence,

00:01:35.479 --> 00:01:36.320
Guo Zixin.

00:01:36.640 --> 00:01:38.120
This is the second young master of the Liu family,

00:01:38.120 --> 00:01:39.080
Liu Sinan.

00:01:40.120 --> 00:01:41.479
How did you two end up together?

00:01:41.479 --> 00:01:42.840
To make a long story short,

00:01:42.840 --> 00:01:43.800
I saved him.

00:01:43.840 --> 00:01:45.500
I begged him to help me escape.

00:01:48.000 --> 00:01:49.039
Thank you, sir.

00:01:49.479 --> 00:01:50.240
No need.

00:01:51.039 --> 00:01:52.840
I pay my respects to you, Young Master.

00:01:52.840 --> 00:01:55.400
I've long heard that the Second Young Master is humble

00:01:55.400 --> 00:01:56.440
and compassionate.

00:01:56.440 --> 00:01:57.720
Now that I've met you,

00:01:58.360 --> 00:02:00.000
I see the rumors are true.

00:02:00.080 --> 00:02:01.760
You all flatter me too much.

00:02:02.720 --> 00:02:04.000
We shouldn't stay here long.

00:02:04.000 --> 00:02:05.160
We should leave quickly.

00:02:05.160 --> 00:02:06.040
Follow me.

00:02:16.720 --> 00:02:17.780
What are you doing?

00:02:20.040 --> 00:02:20.800
Are you okay?

00:02:27.400 --> 00:02:28.760
Let me take care of Yiyu.

00:02:29.480 --> 00:02:30.920
Leave this place as soon as possible.

00:02:30.920 --> 00:02:32.120
The farther you hide, the better.

00:02:32.120 --> 00:02:33.760
So my brother won't catch you.

00:02:33.760 --> 00:02:34.720
He...

00:02:35.640 --> 00:02:37.079
He won't let you go.

00:02:41.280 --> 00:02:43.320
Then I shall take my leave now.

00:02:44.320 --> 00:02:48.579
Thank you, Second Young Master and First Young Mistress, for saving my life.

00:02:57.560 --> 00:02:58.240
Yiyu,

00:02:58.320 --> 00:02:59.320
are you all right?

00:03:00.040 --> 00:03:00.960
Let's go then.

00:03:34.600 --> 00:03:36.200
I haven't even asked you yet.

00:03:36.320 --> 00:03:37.960
We were supposed to get married,

00:03:37.960 --> 00:03:40.420
so why was I sent to the young master instead?

00:03:41.120 --> 00:03:42.040
I swear,

00:03:42.200 --> 00:03:44.240
I knew absolutely nothing about this beforehand.

00:03:44.240 --> 00:03:45.970
Someone drugged me last night,

00:03:46.240 --> 00:03:47.600
and by the time I woke up,

00:03:49.480 --> 00:03:51.140
the wedding was already over.

00:03:52.840 --> 00:03:53.960
I... I swear,

00:03:54.240 --> 00:03:55.240
if I'm lying even slightly,

00:03:55.240 --> 00:03:56.700
may heaven strike me down.

00:03:56.760 --> 00:03:57.960
Don't talk nonsense.

00:03:58.840 --> 00:03:59.840
I believe you.

00:04:00.400 --> 00:04:01.960
What should we do now?

00:04:06.240 --> 00:04:07.240
I absolutely won't let you

00:04:07.240 --> 00:04:08.840
go back to that awful place.

00:04:10.480 --> 00:04:12.080
Whether it offends my father

00:04:12.240 --> 00:04:13.770
or means leaving this home,

00:04:14.880 --> 00:04:16.240
we must be together.

00:04:18.120 --> 00:04:19.000
Yiyu.

00:04:22.400 --> 00:04:23.800
Let's run away together.

00:04:26.680 --> 00:04:28.040
But Sinan,

00:04:28.200 --> 00:04:29.320
I don't want you

00:04:29.480 --> 00:04:31.600
to go against your entire family for me.

00:04:31.600 --> 00:04:32.480
It's not worth it.

00:04:32.480 --> 00:04:33.320
It is worth it.

00:04:34.840 --> 00:04:35.680
For you,

00:04:36.320 --> 00:04:37.520
anything is worth it.

00:04:45.760 --> 00:04:46.840
Catch them!

00:04:50.040 --> 00:04:51.040
Someone's coming!

00:04:51.040 --> 00:04:52.040
Let's go quickly!

00:04:52.040 --> 00:04:53.040
Stop right there!

00:04:53.680 --> 00:04:54.600
Don't run!

00:04:59.120 --> 00:05:00.000
Father!

00:05:02.240 --> 00:05:03.240
Come back with me.

00:05:03.440 --> 00:05:04.320
I won't.

00:05:04.880 --> 00:05:07.280
You clearly know I love the Second Young Master.

00:05:07.280 --> 00:05:10.210
Why are you marrying me off to the First Young Master?

00:05:13.440 --> 00:05:14.240
Come here.

00:05:17.560 --> 00:05:20.600
The master had someone examine the First Young Master.

00:05:20.600 --> 00:05:21.840
They said the First Young Master

00:05:21.840 --> 00:05:24.700
needs to marry a woman with compatible birth charts

00:05:24.760 --> 00:05:25.720
to bring good fortune.

00:05:25.720 --> 00:05:26.440
This way,

00:05:26.760 --> 00:05:29.280
the First Young Master's madness can be cured.

00:05:29.280 --> 00:05:31.040
And you happen to be

00:05:31.120 --> 00:05:33.040
that compatible woman.

00:05:33.560 --> 00:05:35.159
I remember Commander Xu's daughter

00:05:35.159 --> 00:05:37.720
was previously engaged to the First Young Master.

00:05:37.720 --> 00:05:39.480
Wasn't it because he went mad

00:05:39.600 --> 00:05:41.530
that she broke off the engagement?

00:05:43.280 --> 00:05:44.760
I am your daughter.

00:05:44.880 --> 00:05:46.720
How could you do this to me?

00:05:48.480 --> 00:05:50.480
The master has been good to our family,

00:05:50.480 --> 00:05:51.720
very good.

00:05:52.000 --> 00:05:53.800
I'm also the master's confidant

00:05:53.880 --> 00:05:56.120
and the head steward of the Liu family.

00:05:57.000 --> 00:05:59.480
Is it because I'm your adopted daughter

00:06:00.280 --> 00:06:02.410
that you can sell me to the young master

00:06:02.440 --> 00:06:04.640
in exchange for your wealth and status?

00:06:05.320 --> 00:06:06.280
How dare you!

00:06:07.040 --> 00:06:09.280
All these years I've treated you like my own daughter.

00:06:09.280 --> 00:06:10.400
You know that.

00:06:12.280 --> 00:06:13.240
Besides,

00:06:13.560 --> 00:06:15.720
your birth father Jiang Huai and I

00:06:16.000 --> 00:06:17.930
were close friends for many years.

00:06:20.000 --> 00:06:21.730
When your parents were killed,

00:06:21.880 --> 00:06:23.560
I couldn't get there in time.

00:06:23.840 --> 00:06:26.440
It's been weighing on my conscience for years.

00:06:28.400 --> 00:06:30.400
I'm doing this for your own good.

00:06:31.280 --> 00:06:34.440
The young master is the legitimate son of the master.

00:06:34.760 --> 00:06:37.220
The master won't mistreat him in the future.

00:06:37.440 --> 00:06:40.370
Besides, you've already been through the ceremony.

00:06:40.840 --> 00:06:42.320
It's too late to say anything now.

00:06:42.320 --> 00:06:43.440
Come. Follow father home.

00:06:43.440 --> 00:06:44.320
I won't go back.

00:06:44.440 --> 00:06:45.300
Uncle Qianfan.

00:06:47.120 --> 00:06:48.680
